        Constructor that initializes ReportUnit by assigning values to the following parameters
        Parameters:
        reportNum - serial number of current ReportUnit
        fileSize - size of the RAW MS data file (in MB)
        ms1Spectra - number of ms1 spectra
        ms2Spectra - number of ms2 spectra
        measured - day and time at which QC processing of the RAW MS data file begun
        runtime - time (in hh:mm:ss) taken to complete the QC processing of RAW data file
        heatmap - heatmap image file in the bufferedImage format
        ioncount - ioncount image file in the bufferedImage format
